        adicción: juega con responsabilidad. Prohibido para menores de 18 años.
        Línea de ayuda FEJAR: 900 200 225.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="footer-bottom">
      <p>&copy; {year} LegalZone. Todos los derechos reservados.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>

<style>
  .footer {
    background: #090909;
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(212, 168, 83, 0.1);
    padding: 60px 0 30px;
  }

  .footer-top {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 2fr 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 40px;
    margin-bottom: 40px;
  }

  .footer-logo {
    height: 32px;
    width: auto;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .footer-tagline {
    font-size: 14px;
    color: #777;
    line-height: 1.6;
    max-width: 360px;
  }

  .footer-tagline a {
    color: #2ecc71;
    text-decoration: underline;
  }

  .footer-links h4 {
    font-size: 15px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #d4a853;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.5px;
  }

  .footer-links ul {
    list-style: none;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 10px;
  }

  .footer-links a {
    font-size: 14px;
    color: #888;
    transition: color 0.2s;
  }

  .footer-links a:hover {
    color: #fff;
  }

  .footer-badges {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 16px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    margin-bottom: 32px;
    padding-bottom: 32px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.06);
  }

  .badge {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    background: rgba(212, 168, 83, 0.08);
    border: 1px solid rgba(212, 168, 83, 0.2);
    color: #d4a853;
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 700;
    padding: 8px 16px;
    border-radius: 6px;
    min-width: 48px;
  }

  .badge-text {
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .footer-disclaimer {
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }

  .footer-disclaimer p {
    font-size: 12px;
    color: #555;
    text-align: center;
    line-height: 1.7;
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .footer-bottom {
    text-align: center;
  }

  .footer-bottom p {
    font-size: 13px;
    color: #444;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .footer-top {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 32px;
    }
  }
</style>
